rComments: This professor is really good! She cares about students.
She is the best prof for this course.

She is the amazing English Teacher. She knows that everyone here is because they are all on conditional Basis. So she passes everyone with a B grade. She is an amazing lecturer. She gives good Feedback. She replies to email as soon as possible. She marks everything leniently. She is 100% there for you. She Takes every student as her friends.

Amazing prof! I loved her. She's clear and you know what she expects from you. Few short quizzes to do home. Mostly listennings of about 8-10 mins, very interesting. Loved her way to teach and to evaluate. Makes everything look easy. No final exam. I would take her again anytime. The best prof I had since I started University.

Really nice prof! One of my faves so far in my studies. Makes course content easy to understand and the tests reflect what's been taught. Each class looked at a new chapter of the book so there's a lot of reading.
She is very nice but a little bit lost.. But the course in general is easy.
